OL,3,CWelsh education in 'crisis' as fears
OL,4,Cmount that reforms will only make it
OL,5,Cworse
OL,7,FClassrooms in Wales are in a 'crisis'
OL,8,Fas exam results fall to faster than
OL,9,Fany other UK nation, and while reforms
OL,10,Fare coming into place, experts fear
OL,11,Fthey will only further disadvantage
OL,12,Fchildren
OL,14,FWales's Education Minister (and First
OL,15,FMinisterial candidate) Jeremy Miles
OL,16,Fhas announced plans to improve
OL,17,Fattainment and record breaking levels
OL,18,Fof school absences.
