OL,3,CWelsh education in 'crisis' as fears
OL,4,Cmount that reforms will only make it
OL,5,Cworse
OL,7,FThe minister is trying to turn Wales's
OL,8,Fflagging education system around,
OL,9,Fafter pupils recorded the country's
OL,10,Fworst ever Pisa results last month -
OL,11,Fwhen results plummeted faster than in
OL,12,Fany other UK nation.
OL,14,FThe minister told journalists he's
OL,15,Fconfident results will improve, but
OL,16,Fexperts have told ITV News that
OL,17,FWales's education system is in crisis,
OL,18,Fwith fears the government's
OL,19,Fcontroversial new curriculum will make
OL,20,Fthings worse - particularly for the
OL,21,Fpoorest children.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/13
