OL,3,CWelsh education in 'crisis' as fears
OL,4,Cmount that reforms will only make it
OL,5,Cworse
OL,7,FAn exclusive survey of teachers for
OL,8,FITV News found that more than eight in
OL,9,Ften say they don't have enough support
OL,10,Fand that the new curriculum isn't
OL,11,Fraising standards.
OL,13,FHow well children do at school is
OL,14,Foften closely linked to how affluent
OL,15,Ftheir parents are. As the poorest
OL,16,Fnation in the UK, it's no surprise
OL,17,Fthen that Welsh children routinely
OL,18,Fscore badly in international tests
OL,19,Flike Pisa, but this malaise runs
OL,20,Fdeeper.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/13
