OL,3,CWelsh education in 'crisis' as fears
OL,4,Cmount that reforms will only make it
OL,5,Cworse
OL,7,FIn last month's tests, the most
OL,8,Faffluent pupils in Wales had similar
OL,9,Fscores in reading and mathematics to
OL,10,Fthe average in England.
OL,12,FA also found that the difference in
OL,13,Fresults between Welsh pupils from
OL,14,Fpoorer households and their peers at
OL,15,Fage 16 was greater than in England as
OL,16,Fa whole, as well as in even more
OL,17,Fdeprived parts of England.
