OL,3,CWelsh education in 'crisis' as fears
OL,4,Cmount that reforms will only make it
OL,5,Cworse
OL,7,FThe new Curriculum for Wales, rolled
OL,8,Fout since 2019, involves giving
OL,9,Fschools more autonomy over what they
OL,10,Fteach and assess, with the
OL,11,Fresponsibility of designing and
OL,12,Fimplementing it transferred from civil
OL,13,Fservants to teachers. Its emphasis is
OL,14,Fon skills and pupil wellbeing, rather
OL,15,Fthan the procurement of specific
OL,16,Fknowledge.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/13
