OL,3,CWelsh education in 'crisis' as fears
OL,4,Cmount that reforms will only make it
OL,5,Cworse
OL,7,FWhile there has been praise for the
OL,8,Ffreedom this offers teachers, many
OL,9,Ffear it will lead to inconsistency
OL,10,Fbetween schools, and have warned
OL,11,Fsimilar systems has failed elsewhere.
OL,13,FA of the early rollout by Cardiff
OL,14,FUniversity warned that "far from
OL,15,Freducing educational inequalities, the
OL,16,Fnew Curriculum for Wales may actually
OL,17,Fexacerbate them".
