OL,3,CWelsh education in 'crisis' as fears
OL,4,Cmount that reforms will only make it
OL,5,Cworse
OL,7,FOne of the authors, Dr Nigel Newton,
OL,8,Ftold ITV News there was "no evidence"
OL,9,Ftheir concerns had been addressed by
OL,10,Fthe Welsh government.
OL,12,FWales's new curriculum is very similar
OL,13,Fto that implemented more than a decade
OL,14,Fago in Scotland, which was recently
OL,15,Fcriticised by Lindsay Paterson,
OL,16,Femeritus professor of education policy
OL,17,Fat the University of Edinburgh as
OL,18,F"badly thought-out", and an
OL,19,F"inescapable culprit" in the "severe
OL,20,Fdecline" of Scotland's recent PISA
OL,21,Fresults.
