OL,3,CWelsh education in 'crisis' as fears
OL,4,Cmount that reforms will only make it
OL,5,Cworse
OL,7,FSimilar curricula in Finland, New
OL,8,FZealand and Australia also saw
OL,9,Fdeclines in results which subsequently
OL,10,Fled to reform.
OL,12,FEducationalists agree that curricula
OL,13,Flike these often require more
OL,14,Fresources to succeed, but the Welsh
OL,15,Fgovernment has overseen successive
OL,16,Freal term cuts to the education
OL,17,Fbudget. Last week 87% of headteachers
OL,18,Fin Wales warned they would need to cut
OL,19,Ftheir budgets next year.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/13
