OL,3,CWelsh education in 'crisis' as fears
OL,4,Cmount that reforms will only make it
OL,5,Cworse
OL,7,FAsked today whether international
OL,8,Fresults have given the minister pause
OL,9,Ffor thought over the new curriculum,
OL,10,Fthe minister told ITV News he was
OL,11,Fconfident it was part of the answer to
OL,12,Fimproving standards.
OL,14,F"The reform programme that we have is,
OL,15,Fyes about the curriculum, but about a
OL,16,Frange of other reforms as well
OL,17,Fincluding around school improvement
OL,18,Fand teaching. And those reforms have
OL,19,Factually been designed together with
OL,20,Fthe OECD which is the organisation
OL,21,Fwhich runs the Pisa tests."
