OL,3,CWelsh education in 'crisis' as fears
OL,4,Cmount that reforms will only make it
OL,5,Cworse
OL,7,FThe minister cited New Zealand and
OL,8,FCanada as countries who have been
OL,9,Fsuccessful after undergoing similar
OL,10,Fcurriculum reforms, however, both
OL,11,Fcountries have seen a consistent
OL,12,Fdecline in their Pisa scores over the
OL,13,Fpast decade.
OL,15,FAsked whether he had read the report
OL,16,Fby Cardiff University warning that the
OL,17,Fnew curriculum could worsen the
OL,18,Fattainment gap, the minister didn't
OL,19,Frespond.
