OL,7,FThe Welsh government is clearly
OL,8,Ftotally committed to its new
OL,9,Fcurriculum, but as international
OL,10,Fevidence emerges that similar systems
OL,11,Fare failing, many fear that the
OL,12,Fgovernment may have backed the wrong
OL,13,Fhorse.
